channel.title: The Women's Football Show
channel.desc: Highlights from the finalweekend of the Women's Super League 2024/25 season as Chelsea host Liverpool, Manchester United travel to Arsenal and Manchester City welcome Crystal Palace. The other fixtures are Aston Villa v Brighton & Hove Albion, Everton v Tottenham Hotspur and Leicester City v West Ham United.
